38-15：05：59\r\n一身穿黑色上衣之男子從監視器畫面下方出現，走至監視器畫面\r\n上方三名男子旁。","JFULLPDF":"https://data.judicial.gov.tw/jdg/api/JDocFile/HLDM/109%2c%e6%98%93%2c217%2c20211116%2c1/pdf"},"JID":"HLDM,109,易,217,20211116,1","JYEAR":"109","JCASE":"易","JNO":"217","JDATE":"20211116","JTITLE":"竊盜"}